# {{ project_name }} — frontend

SvelteKit + shadcn-svelte (bun, adapter-node, Tailwind v4). Talks to the backend at `/api`.

## Develop

```bash
bun install
bun run dev        # proxies /api → http://localhost:8000
```

## Test

```bash
bun run test:unit   # vitest (jsdom) component/unit tests
bunx playwright install    # once
bun run test:e2e    # Playwright smoke (builds + previews)
```

## Build

```bash
bun run build       # adapter-node → build/
node build          # run (set PORT / ORIGIN in production)
```

## Auth

Login posts to `/api/login`; the returned JWT is stored in an httpOnly `auth_token`
cookie by `src/routes/login/+page.server.ts`. `src/hooks.server.ts` injects it as a
Bearer header on server-side `/api` calls. `/items` is guarded and redirects to `/login`.
